1) Download theme (-s),
2) Open Kvantum Manager,
3) Click "Select a Kvantum theme folder",
4) Locate and Choose the theme folder you just downloaded (e.g. Mojave-dark),
5) Click "Install this theme",
6) Click "Change/Delete theme",
7) Select your theme (e.g. Mojave-dark).

Go to  System Settings=> Application Style, select kvantum & Apply it.
